- [ ] Use `npm run lint` to validate import paths and code quality.
- [ ] Use `npm run type-check` for TypeScript validation.
- [ ] Only mention build commands in the context of actual deployment.
- [ ] Prefer faster, incremental validation tools over comprehensive builds.

This ensures efficient development workflow and prevents unnecessary resource consumption during code validation.
